      <npc_text>"About time you showed up. It's a new day out there. Serenas rules the city now. Or thinks that he does. Pavola's men are keeping order, not that anyone's unhappy about Gaelius' sudden departure. Except for the Boatmen, of course, but they had it coming."</npc_text>
