      <npc_text>Surrounded by guards, Levir walks through the city like a shah, people scrambling to get out of his way. Only now you begin to realize his status and power.

He takes you to a villa overlooking the palace district. The villa is surrounded by the Aurelian legionaries, but they too step aside when Levir approaches. Leaving his own guards to wait outside, Levir goes through the door without any hesitation.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>dlgFadeToThisPart();</string>
        <string>setWindowImage(tg6_meeting_01);</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>Follow him.</text>
          <def_link>2918</def_link>
