    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>None</portrait>
      <speaker_name>None</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>You see two men standing in the middle room. They glance at you, then look at Levir questioningly.

“&lt;He/She&gt; earned &lt;his/her&gt; right to be here,” says Levir without elaborating, although it’s not hard to figure out what he’s referring to. “&lt;charname&gt;, meet Lord Senna and master Strabos. They rule Maadoran now, thanks to you.”

“Except for the Slums,” says Strabos. “As agreed, the Slums are yours and we lay no claims on it.” “As long as order is maintained,” adds Lord Senna. “We don’t want chaos and we don’t want any spillover. Keep it clean.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>dlgFadeShortToThisPart();</string>
        <string>setWindowImage(tg6_meeting_02);</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
