    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Senna</portrait>
      <speaker_name>Senna</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“Now, what about the situation in Ganezzar? We want it handled fast,” says Senna.

“&lt;charname&gt; will take care of it,” says Levir. “That’s why I brought &lt;him/her&gt; here. Just tell &lt;him/her&gt; what needs to be done.”

“Very well,” nods Senna. “The Aurelian forces are heading toward Ganezzar as we speak. Castle Ganezzar was built to last. A siege will take too long and cost too much. We can't afford that. We need a decisive victory that will reassure the good people of Maadoran that their city is in the right hands.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“How can I be of service?”</text>
          <def_link>2920</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>2919</UID>
